data.description: Beautiful 4 bedroom 3 1/2 bath home in Edinburg, Tx. Front entry features a large courtyard. Inside home features an open concept. Kitchen equipped with black stainless steel appliances. Master bath features double vanities and a walk in closet. You can also find a casita in the back yard and can use as a play room or a guest house. Home owners can enjoy subdivision amenities which include: swimming pool & gated entry to subdivision and a private park.
